<p>Question: what constitutes the Working Class? Anyone who works for wages? Or ? We really need to be clear about this, because the way US narratives are conceived, there is no working class or upper class, all is middle class, &#8220;Hard Working&#8221; at that. And we know that&#8217;s not true, don&#8217;t we?</p>
