				<p>There won&#8217;t be a working class or lower class party in America as long as most Americans accept the teaching they received that working classness or lower classness is embarrassing and shameful.</p>
<p>     The only way for the ClassShamed American to get over their ClassShame is to break through it or work through it on their own.    Maybe helping eachother in sets and groups.    But no help will come from the ClassProud Middles and Uppers.</p>
<p>      And the Working Class will have to get over its fear and loathing and self-defensive contempt for the Lower Classes.    They will have to learn for themselves that hating and despising the Lower Classes will not save them from being demoted into the Lower Classes whenever the ClassProud Middles and/or Uppers feel like demoting them.</p>
<p>     If the Working Classes ever understand themselves to be temporarily-better-off Lower Class people, then they will have made some initial progress towards understanding their position and situation.</p>
